== Locale-updater ==

1/ Install this [addon](https://github.com/downloads/ochameau/locale-updater/locale-updater.xpi),
2/ Open about:addons,
3/ Click on "Update l10n" button next to the Jetpack/Addon-SDK addon you want to translate,
4/ Select one or multiple .properties file(s) you want to test,
5/ The addon is automatically uninstalled and reinstalled with updated localization files.
